# Optional build-time engine config for SmartBooks.
#
# If set, these win over the hardcoded demo defaults (127.0.0.1:7777 +
# dev-token) but lose to any `Connect` form override stored in
# localStorage. See src/lib/config.ts::resolveEngineConfig.
#
# Copy to `.env.local` (gitignored) and fill in.

# VITE_HOUSTON_ENGINE_BASE=http://127.0.0.1:7777
# VITE_HOUSTON_ENGINE_TOKEN=dev-token
